title: Headaches - I've had my Pixel 5 for 2 weeks and keep getting headaches after using it, anyone else?
content:
I keep getting headaches like I've never experienced after I use my new Pixel 5 (screen use not telephone calls) I have turned down the brightness, I wondered if anyone else is experiencing the same?
I've had my phone for about 2 weeks and these headaches coincide.
